#: ../../docs/user_manual/map_views/index.rst:5
msgid "Visualizing Maps"
msgstr "Vizuelizacija karata"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/map_views/index.rst:7
msgid ""
"Creating maps is one of the \"business ends\" of QGIS. Map views are "
"canvases to visualize spatial layers loaded in the project, with the various"
" rendering settings applied to them. They can be of :ref:`2D "
"<label_mapview>` or :ref:`3D <label_3dmapview>` type or plotted along a "
":ref:`profile line <label_elevation_profile_view>`, show different scale or "
"extent, or display a different set of the loaded layers thanks to :ref:`map "
"themes <map_themes>`."
msgstr ""
"Pravljenje karata je jedna od „praktičnih svrha“ QGIS-a. Prikazi karte su "
"platna za vizuelizaciju prostornih slojeva učitanih u projektu, sa "
"primenjenim raznim podešavanjima iscrtavanja. Mogu biti :ref:`2D "
"<label_mapview>` ili :ref:`3D <label_3dmapview>` tipa ili iscrtani duž "
":ref:`profilne linije <label_elevation_profile_view>`, prikazivati različitu"
" razmeru ili obuhvat, ili prikazivati različit skup učitanih slojeva "
"zahvaljujući :ref:`temama karte <map_themes>`."
